quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  57,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  57,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh ki hai har uss cheez ne jo zameen aur asmano mein hai, aur wohi zabardast Dana hai"
  57,2,"zameen aur asmano ki saltanat ka maalik wohi hai, zindagi bkhshta hai aur mout deta hai, aur har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  57,3,"wohi awwal bhi hai aur aakhir bhi, zahir bhi hai aur makhfi bhi, aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  57,4,wohi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya aur phir arsh par jalva farma howa uss ke ilm mein hai jo kuch zameen mein jata hai aur jo kuch is se nikalta hai aur jo kuch aasman se utartaa hai aur jo kuch uss mein charhata hai woh tumahray sath hai jahan bhi tum ho jo kaam bhi karte ho usay woh dekh raha hai
  57,5,wohi zameen aur asmano ki badshahi ka maalik hai aur tamam mamlaat faislay ke liye usi ki taraf rujoo kiye jatay hain
  57,6,"wohi raat ko din mein aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai, aur dilon ke chupay hue raaz taq jaanta hai"
  57,7,imaan lao Allah aur is ke rasool par aur kharch karo unn cheezon mein se jin par is ne tum ko khalifa banaya hai jo log tum mein se imaan layein ge aur maal kharch karen ge un ke liye bara ajar hai
  57,8,tumhe kya ho gaya hai ke tum Allah par imaan nahi laatay halaank rasool tumhe apne rab par imaan laane ki dawat day raha hai aur woh tum se ehad le chuka hai agar tum waqai maan-ne walay ho
  57,9,"woh Allah hi to hai jo apne bande par saaf saaf ayatain nazil kar raha hai taakay tumhe tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein le aeye, aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah tum par nihayat shafeeq aur meharban hai"
  57,10,aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum Allah ki raah mein kharch nahi karte halaank zameen aur asmano ki meeras Allah hi ke liye hai tum mein se jo log fatah ke baad kharch aur jehaad karen ge woh kabhi unn logon ke barabar nahi ho satke jinhon ne fatah se pehlay kharch aur jehaad kya hai unn ka darja baad mein kharch aur jehaad karne walon se barh kar hai agarchay Allah ne dono hi se achay waday farmaiye hain jo kuch tum karte ho Allah is se ba khabar hai
  57,11,"kon hai jo Allah ko qarz day? acha qarz, taakay Allah usay kayi gina barha kar wapas day, aur uss ke liye behtareen ajar hai"
  57,12,"uss din jabkay tum momin mardon aur aurton ko dekho ge ke un ka noor unn ke agay agay aur un ke dayen janib daud raha hoga ( un se kaha jaye ga ke )"" aaj basharat hai tumahray liye"" jannaten hongi jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hongi, jin mein woh hamesha rahen ge yahi hai barri kamyabi"
  57,13,"uss roz munafiq mardon aur aurton ka haal yeh hoga ke woh mominoun se kahin ge zara hamari taraf dekho taakay hum tumahray noor se kuch faida utthayen, magar un se kaha jaye ga peechay hatt jao, apna noor kahin aur talaash karo phir un ke darmain aik deewar haail kar di jaye gi jis mein aik darwaaza hoga uss darwazay ke andar rehmat hogi aur bahar azaab"
  57,14,"woh mominoun se pukaar pukaar kar kahin ge kya hum tumahray sath nah thay? momin jawab den ge haan, magar tum ne apne aap ko khud ftne mein dala, mauqa parasti ki, shak mein parre rahay, aur jhooti tawaquaat tumhe fraib deti rahen, yahan taq ke Allah ka faisla aa gaya, aur aakhir waqt taq woh bara dhokay baz tumhe Allah ke maamla mein dhoka deta raha"
  57,15,"lehaza aaj nah tum se koi Fidya qubool kya jaye ga aur nah unn logon se jinhon ne khula khula kufar kya tha tumhara thikana jahannum hai, wohi tumhari khabar Gary karne wali hai aur yeh bad tareen injaam hai"
  57,16,"kya imaan laane walon ke liye abhi woh waqt nahi aaya ke unn ke dil Allah ke zikar se pighalen aur uss ke nazil kardah haq ke agay jhuken aur woh unn logon ki terhan nah ho jayen jinhein pehlay kitaab di gayi thi, phir aik lambi muddat unn par guzar gayi to un ke dil sakht ho gay aur aaj un mein se aksar fasik banay hue hain ?"
  57,17,"khoob jaan lau ke, Allah zameen ko uss ki mout ke baad zindagi bkhshta hai, hum ne nishanain tum ko saaf saaf dikha di hain, shayad ke tum aqal se kaam lau"
  57,18,"mardon aur aurton mein se jo log sadqat dainay walay hain aur jinhon ne Allah ko qarz husn diya hai, unn ko yaqeenan kayi gina barha kar diya jaye ga aur un ke liye behtareen ajar hai"
  57,19,"aur jo log Allah aur is ke Rasolo-n par imaan laaye hain wohi apne rab ke nazdeek Seddiq aur shaheed hain, unn ke liye unn ka ajar aur unn ka noor hai aur jin logon ne kufar kya hai aur hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya hai woh dozakhi hain"
  57,20,khoob jaan lau ke yeh duniya ki zindagi is ke siwa kuch nahi ke aik khail aur dil lagi aur zahiri tape taap aur tumhara aapas mein aik dosray par fakhr jatana aur maal o aulaad mein aik dosray se barh jaane ki koshish karna hai is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik barish ho gayi to is se peda honay wali nabataat ko dekh kar kaasht car khush ho gay phir wohi khaiti pick jati hai aur tum dekhte ho ke woh zard ho gayi phir woh bhus ban kar reh jati hai iss ke bar aks akhirat woh jagah hai jahan sakht azaab hai aur Allah ki mughfirat aur is ki khushnodi hai duniya ki zindagi aik dhokay ki tatti ke siwa kuch nahi
  57,21,"dorro aur aik dosray se agay bherne ki koshish karo apne rab ki mughfirat aur uss ki jannat ki taraf jis ki wusat aasman o zameen jaisi hai, jo muhayya ki gayi hai unn logon ke liye jo Allah aur uss ke Rasolo-n par imaan laaye hon yeh Allah ka fazl hai, jisay chahta hai ataa farmata hai, aur Allah barray fazl wala hai"
  57,22,koi museebat aisi nahi hai jo zameen mein ya tumahray apne nafs par nazil hoti ho aur hum ne is ko peda karne se pehlay aik kitaab mein likh nah rakha ho aisa karna Allah ke liye bohat aasaan kaam hai
  57,23,( yeh sab kuch is liye hai ) taakay jo kuch bhi nuqsaan tumhe ho is par tum dil shakista nah ho aur jo kuch Allah tumhe ataa farmaiye is par phool nah jao Allah aisay logon ko pasand nahi karta jo apne aap ko barri cheez samajte hain aur fakhr jatate hain
  57,24,jo khud bukhal karte hain aur dosaron ko bukhal par aksate hain ab agar koi ro gardani karta hai to Allah be niaz aur Satudah sifaat hai
  57,25,"hum ne apne Rasolo-n ko saaf saaf nshanyon aur Hadayat ke sath bheja, aur unn ke sath kitaab aur maizaan nazil ki taakay log insaaf par qaim hon, aur loha utaara jis mein bara zor hai aur logon ke liye munafe hain yeh is liye kya gaya hai ke Allah ko maloom ho jaye ke kon uss ko dekhe baghair is ki aur uss ke Rasolo-n ki madad karta hai yaqeenan Allah barri qowat wala aur zabardast hai"
  57,26,hum ne Nooh aur ibrahim ko bheja aur unn dono ki nasal mein nabuwat aur kitaab rakh di phir un ki aulaad mein se kisi ne hadaayat ikhtiyar ki aur bohat se fasik ho gay
  57,27,"unn ke baad hum ne pay Dur pay apne rasool beje, aur un sab ke baad eesa Ibn maryam ko maboos kya aur uss ko injeel ataa ki aur jin logon ne is ki pairwi ikhtiyar ki unn ke dilon mein hum ne taras aur reham daal diya aur rahbaniyat unhon ne khud ijaad karli, hum ne ussay unn par farz nahi kya tha, magar Allah ki khushnodi ki talab mein unhon ne aap hi yeh bidat nikaali aur phir is ki pabandi karne ka jo haq tha usay ada nah kya unn mein se jo log imaan laaye hue thay unn ka ajar hum ne un ko ataa kya, magar un mein se aksar log fasik hain"
  57,28,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par imaan lao, Allah tumhe apni rehmat ka dohra hissa ataa farmaiye ga aur tumhe woh noor bakhshay ga jis ki roshni mein tum chalo ge, aur tumahray qasoor maaf kar day ga, Allah bara maaf karne wala aur meharban hai"
  57,29,"( tum ko yeh rawish ikhtiyar karni chahiye ) taakay ahal kitaab ko maloom ho jaye ke Allah ke fazl par unn ka koi ajarah nahi hai, aur yeh ke Allah ka fazl is ke apne hi haath mein hai, jisay chahta hai ataa farmata hai, aur woh barray fazl wala hai"
